Tga '''Talimant''' (Deutsch s talimant) yat tutlayt ittuysawaln ɣ wammas n urubba. tga talimant tutlayt tunṣibt ɣ [[Lalman|waliman]], tg yat zɣ tutlayin tunṣibin ɣ ustrayk; swisra; iffus n tirul (iṭalya); tagrawt tamslalimant n bljika, luksmburg, d liktnctayn.

